OL,3,CMan arrested after out-of-control dog
OL,4,Cseriously injures two people
OL,6,FA man is being questioned after a dog
OL,7,Fcaused serious injuries to two people
OL,8,Fin Crawley on Saturday.
OL,10,FOfficers from Sussex Police were
OL,11,Fcalled to Sunningdale Court in the
OL,12,FSouthgate area of the town at around
OL,13,F1pm , following reports of a dog that
OL,14,Fwas seriously out of control.
OL,16,FA spokesman from the force said armed
OL,17,Fofficers were sent to the scene, and
OL,18,Fthe Cane Corso breed dog was secured
OL,19,Fand assessed before being "humanely
OL,20,Fput to sleep in the interest of public
OL,21,Fsafety and animal welfare."
