OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1783950571
OL,3,CMan arrested after out-of-control dog
OL,4,Cseriously injures two people
OL,6,FA 27-year-old man, believed to be the
OL,7,Fanimal's owner, was arrested in
OL,8,Fconnection with the incident and
OL,9,Fremains in custody..
OL,11,FThe two injured people required
OL,12,Fmedical treatment.
OL,14,FSussex Police said it was
OL,15,Finvestigating the circumstances and
OL,16,Furged anyone with relevant information
OL,17,Fto get in touch.
